{"tid":651714,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"京阿尼歷代黑長直Top 3","createTime":"2018-05-03T09:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T08:08:31.000Z","uid":183666,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc98162631f1c0fcfc6d38eb3804120cfd796ab","tid":651714,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"No. 3　植野 直花（うえの なおか）<br />\n將也小學時的同班女同學，也是少數和將也談的來的女生。對硝子反感的同學之一，指出將也該負起助聽器賠償問題的同學之一，事件過後與將也關係逐漸疏遠。中學與將也同校，高中則與佐原同校，爾後與將也再次相遇時表示中學時期就想與將也說話，其實一直喜歡著將也。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://koenokatachi-movie.com/img/character/ueno-img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkoenokatachi-movie.com%2Fimg%2Fcharacter%2Fueno-img.png&h=f4d80c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DUT9j1qVAAY3QL6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDUT9j1qVAAY3QL6.jpg&h=03d7e57f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b82f6e76294bbe5085574281972f7ba908a25a1","tid":651714,"uid":86762,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:56:01.000Z","msg":"我估有千反田同高坂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ff5686367c121e26366ee49a7ce27569954b8c","tid":651714,"uid":37890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"No.1 高坂麗奈"},{"pid":"272102dd514568f29e2b8a0248a819676b5000d8","tid":651714,"uid":45373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"33ff5686367c121e26366ee49a7ce27569954b8c","tid":651714,"uid":37890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"No.1 高坂麗奈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"no.1 mio <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc3d5e3107b1cbb98456419bf088b0ef90fced1","tid":651714,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"一樣樣"},{"pid":"3c1c7efe16f8b724d9e1c57c5bd2dfbd70be3b8b","tid":651714,"uid":84208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"千田反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5554a985cd0ee6df2e5417c84ac6aab6069d38ed","tid":651714,"uid":183666,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"No.2　名瀬 美月（なせ みつき）<br />\n名瀨家的次女，長月市立高中二年級生，劇場版未來篇起為三年級生，文藝部的部長。<br />\n平日主要任務是監視身為半妖夢的秋人。<br />\n興趣是戲弄秋人。<br />\n異界士能力也是操縱空間，但是力量比博臣稍弱。作為彌補，馴養著一隻名為「小番薯」的妖夢，以指揮牠與妖夢戰鬥作為主要攻擊手段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tv.anime-kyokai.com/img/character/mitsuki.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.anime-kyokai.com%2Fimg%2Fcharacter%2Fmitsuki.png&h=a99120a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MAVHVDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMAVHVDV.jpg&h=17af790f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0886eeb59dd30aaabf0de53e8f01aec8648d22e1","tid":651714,"uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"睇到第2位就知shit"},{"pid":"ab24868f453dc5d5b45bbacdcb4216583d483b8c","tid":651714,"uid":159746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ff5686367c121e26366ee49a7ce27569954b8c","tid":651714,"uid":37890,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:57:04.000Z","msg":"No.1 高坂麗奈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b78db98d2640c4dea90fb92572b46a4e83c2189","tid":651714,"uid":183666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0886eeb59dd30aaabf0de53e8f01aec8648d22e1","tid":651714,"uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"睇到第2位就知shit"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T